# Google OAuth 2.0 credentials
# Get these from: https://console.cloud.google.com → APIs & Services → Credentials
# Enable the "Google Drive API" for your project first.
#
# Create 3 OAuth 2.0 Client IDs:
#   1. Web application          → EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_WEB_CLIENT_ID
#   2. iOS (bundle: com.feemovision.feemobudget)     → EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_IOS_CLIENT_ID
#   3. Android (package: com.feemovision.feemobudget) → EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_ANDROID_CLIENT_ID
#
# For Android you'll also need the SHA-1 fingerprint from:
#   eas credentials --platform android

